<Base title="SocialProof for Realtors — Client Testimonials That Generate Referrals | SocialProof" description="Real estate agents: automate client testimonial collection after every closing. Display reviews on your agent website and turn happy buyers and sellers into referrals. Free to start.">
  <main>
    <section style="max-width:860px;margin:0 auto;padding:3rem 1.5rem;">
      <h1 style="font-size:2.5rem;font-weight:800;line-height:1.2;margin-bottom:1rem;">
        Social Proof for Realtors
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1.2rem;color:#555;margin-bottom:2rem;">
        Buyers and sellers interview multiple agents before choosing. Your track record matters — but what matters more is what past clients say about working with you. SocialProof helps you capture testimonials after every closing and display them on your site while the market keeps moving.
      </p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Why testimonials are the #1 trust signal for real estate agents</h2>
      <p>Real estate is the biggest financial decision most families make. They're not just picking an agent — they're deciding who guides that decision. At that stakes level, people need reassurance from people like them. A client who says "she found us a house in 14 days in a hot market" is worth more than any awards or designations you can list.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:1rem;">Most agents have plenty of happy clients. Most never ask for a testimonial. The agents with the most visible social proof win the most referrals — not necessarily the best agents.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">High-converting testimonial themes for realtors</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Market expertise:</strong> "She knew every neighborhood we looked in — helped us avoid two bad deals."</li>
        <li><strong>Negotiation:</strong> "Got us $18k below asking in a seller's market. Phenomenal negotiator."</li>
        <li><strong>Communication:</strong> "Never felt out of the loop. Texts back within the hour, always."</li>
        <li><strong>First-time buyer support:</strong> "Held our hand through the whole process. Made it feel manageable."</li>
        <li><strong>Selling results:</strong> "Listed on Thursday, had offers by Saturday, sold over asking. She's a wizard."</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">How SocialProof works for real estate agents</h2>
      <ol style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>After closing</strong>, send your collection link in the congratulations email or via text.</li>
        <li><strong>Clients submit their testimonial</strong> in 2 minutes — no login, no app download.</li>
        <li><strong>Approve with one click</strong> from your phone or laptop.</li>
        <li><strong>Display automatically</strong> on your agent website, bio page, or landing pages.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Best timing: ask right after closing</h2>
      <p>The window for a great testimonial is narrow. Clients are most enthusiastic in the first week after closing — they're excited, grateful, and not yet buried in moving logistics. Drop your SocialProof link in the closing gift message or post-close email. That's where you'll get your most detailed, emotional responses.</p>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Where to display testimonials on your agent site</h2>
      <ul style="padding-left:1.5rem;line-height:1.9;">
        <li><strong>Homepage hero</strong> — right next to your headshot and market stats</li>
        <li><strong>About page</strong> — proof that your bio claims are real</li>
        <li><strong>Buyer/Seller guides</strong> — social proof at the educational moment</li>
        <li><strong>Contact page</strong> — reduce hesitation when someone is deciding whether to reach out</li>
        <li><strong>Listing pages</strong> — signal you're the right agent for this neighborhood</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 style="font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:700;margin-top:2.5rem;">Free forever for one widget</h2>
      <p>SocialProof is free forever for one active widget. Collect unlimited testimonials, approve them, and display them on your site. When you want multiple widgets for different pages or audiences (buyers vs sellers, different markets), Pro is $9/month.</p>

